---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import IconWhatsapp from '~icons/logos/whatsapp-icon';
---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-r from-dark/90 to-black/70 z-10"></div>
    <Image
      src="/hero-bg.png"
      alt="Pães recém saídos do forno"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      width={4128}
      height={3096}
    />
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-lg max-w-4xl animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-100">
      Atendimento e qualidade <br/> é a nossa marca
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-secondary max-w-2xl mb-10 drop-shadow-md animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200 lg:leading-relaxed">
      Pão quentinho a toda hora, buffet self-service, lanches caprichados e pizzas saborosas. Tudo feito com muito carinho para você e sua família.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-300">
      <a href="#" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white hover:text-accent transition-colors font-medium text-lg drop-shadow-md bg-dark/40 px-6 py-3 rounded-full backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20">
        <IconWhatsapp class="w-6 h-6" />
        <span>Fale Conosco</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-dark transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg text-lg">
        Acessar Cardápio
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


